long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Find ai text from ChatGPT and other language models without copying and pasting into a detector.

 Like a grammar checker extension but for ai generated text. Checks your entire webpage for ChatGPT content and highlights it on the page. 

Use Deep Find to discover fake emails, news articles, bots in your social media feed,  or papers written by ai. 

Disclaimer: detection models are not 100% accurate and should not be used as the only criteria for making a decision on whether text is written by ai.
